s="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="兰布里尼女孩、Wunderhorse 和劳伦·梅伯里。图片来源：Lorne Thomson 和 Xavi Torrent，来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lambrini-Girls-Wunderhorse-and-Lauren-Mayberry-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauren-mayberry">Lauren Mayberry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a>等乐队已被宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/the-great-escape">《The Great Escape 2024》</a>的表演者。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-10-best-new-artists-the-great-escape-2023-radar-3443679">我们在 2023 年大逃亡中看到的 10 个最佳新表演</a></strong></li></ul><p>一年一度的布莱顿音乐节于今年 5 月 15 日至 18 日举行，吸引了来自世界各地的崭露头角的艺术家，他们的阵容中新增了 150 位新人，涵盖流行、电子、朋克、说唱等领域。</p><p>最新成员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">Soft Play</a> （以前称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slaves">Slaves</a> ）、Bradley Simpson（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/the-vamps">The Vamps</a>的主唱）、 <a href="/artists/been-stellar">Been Stellar</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-roberts">Fred Roberts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/love-fame-tragedy">Love Fame Tragedy</a>和<a href="/artists/milk.">Milk。</a>和更多。</p><p>音乐节还为无法整个周末参加的粉丝发行了个人单日和两日门票。单日票价格为 47.50 英镑至 63.90 英镑，两日票价格为 92.25 英镑，周末通票价格为 86.13 英镑至 102.75 英镑<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-great-escape-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F1832966">，请访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4LcnOVJ3UC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,