摇滚刺激”</a> 。</p><p> 2023 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pretenders">The Pretenders</a>在 The Great Escape 音乐节上开启了他们亲密的英国俱乐部巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pretenders-debut-new-songs-during-intimate-gig-at-the-great-escape-3443028">并首次推出了新歌曲</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-lauren-mayberry-wunderhorse-lambrini-girls-lead-150-new-names-for-the-great-escape-2024-3597622">Kneecap、Lauren Mayberry、Wunderhorse、Lambrini Girls 领衔的《The Great Escape 2024》的 150 个新名字</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
