ttps://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/remedy-plans-to-expand-alan-wake-franchise-3588576">发展和扩大这些特许经营权将是我们未来的关键部分</a>，”Remedy 首席执行官 Tero Virtala 说道。</p><p> 2022 年，Remedy 确认正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/control-2-is-in-development-but-release-will-take-a-while-3347710">制作<em>《Control》</em>的续集。</a></p><p>本周早些时候，微软发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X</a>主机的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-releases-limited-edition-spongebob-squarepants-xbox-3597004">新限量版<i>海绵宝宝</i></a>特别版。</p><p>其他新闻方面，新黑色射击游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/el-paso-elsewhere"><i>《El Paso, Everywhere</i></a> 》背后的工作室<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/strange-scaffold">Strange Scaffold</a>已经确认了他们下一个项目的细节—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/el-paso-everywhere-studio-announces-new-fantasy-kidnapping-game-life-eater-3597560">一款名为<i>Life Eater</i>的恐怖奇幻绑架游戏。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/control-ultimate-edition-heads-up-marchs-xbox-game-pass-additions-3597584">“Control Ultimate Edition”帖子预告了 3 月份的 Xbox Game Pass 新增内容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
